      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
        <p>
          <img class="example" src="https://generative-placeholders.glitch.me/image?width=400&height=300&style=123">      
        </p>
        <pre><code class="html">&#x3C;img src=&#x22;https://generative-placeholders.glitch.me/image?width=400&#x26;height=300&#x26;style=123&#x22;&#x3E;</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h3>
      Tweak the look
    </h3>    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-12">
        <p>
          The image generator uses the <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/nice-color-palettes">nice-color-palettes</a> node package to pick a random color palette. You can choose a specific palette by passing an index of one of the top 100 palettes as <code>colors</code>.
        </p>
        <p>
          <img class="example" src="https://generative-placeholders.glitch.me/image?width=400&height=300&style=cellular-automata&colors=2">      
        </p>
        <pre><code class="html">&#x3C;img src=&#x22;https://generative-placeholders.glitch.me/image?width=400&#x26;height=300&#x26;style=cellular-automata&#x26;cells=20&#x26;colors=2&#x22;&#x3E;</code></pre>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-12">
        <p>
          Certain styles have additional parameters that you can adjust.
        </p>
        <h4>
          Cellular automata
        </h4>
        <ul>
          <li><code>cells</code>: number of cells on each line</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          <img class="example" src="https://generative-placeholders.glitch.me/image?width=400&height=300&style=cellular-automata&cells=10">      
        </p>
        <pre><code class="html">&#x3C;img src=&#x22;https://generative-placeholders.glitch.me/image?width=400&#x26;height=300&#x26;style=cellular-automata&#x26;cells=10&#x22;&#x3E;</code></pre>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-12">
        <h4>
          Triangles
        </h4>
        <ul>
          <li><code>gap</code>: controls the size of the triangles</li>
        </ul>        
        <p>
          <img class="example" src="https://generative-placeholders.glitch.me/image?width=400&height=300&style=triangles&gap=100">
        </p>
        <pre><code class="html">&#x3C;img src=&#x22;https://generative-placeholders.glitch.me/image?width=400&#x26;height=300&#x26;style=triangles&#x26;gap=100&#x22;&#x3E;</code></pre>        
      </div>
    </div>
